trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemCreated"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemDataBound"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemCreated"> </xref> och <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemDataBound"> </xref> händelser.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemCreated?displayProperty=fullName> event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapNodeItem> is created by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemCreated?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen inträffar när en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapNodeItem>skapas av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapNodeItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemCreated?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemDataBound?displayProperty=fullName> event is raised when `DataBind` is called on the item during a call to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.CreateControlHierarchy%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemDataBound?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen inträffar när `DataBind` anropas på objektet under ett anrop till <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.CreateControlHierarchy%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.CreateControlHierarchy%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapPath.ItemDataBound?displayProperty=fullName>
